===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|freendly}}, {{m|enm|frendli}}, {{m|enm|frendely}}, {{m|enm|frendlich}}, from {{inh|en|ang|frēondlīċ}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*frijōndlīkaz}}, equivalent to {{suffix|en|friend|ly|id2=adjectival}}. Cognate with {{cog|stq|früntelk}}, {{m|stq|fjuntelk|t=friendly}}, {{cog|fy|freonlik|t=friendly}}, {{cog|nl|vriendelijk|t=friendly}}, {{cog|nds-de|fründelk}}, {{m|nds-de|frünnelk|t=friendly}}, {{cog|de|freundlich|t=friendly}}.

